WEEKLY STATS
[STRAIGHT UP]
TRACK WEEKLY AND SEASON STATS
MAIN MENU
MAIN MENU
BASIC GAME PLAY

TO START:
Select the winner of each game from Week 1 to Week 17 of the season (256 total games).

This can be done from the MAKE PICKS tab on the MAIN MENU.

After all picks are made based the teams YOU believe will win, select the SUBMIT button to enter your picks.
NEXT:
From the MAIN MENU, select the STANDINGS tab to view results of the selections that you made for the entire season.

Every team's win/loss record will display as would in any typical standings.
(Note: Each team's position in the standings will remain in the same spot regardless of the record.)
MAIN MENU
Tap on a team name in the STANDINGS to view that team's full weekly schedule.
MAIN MENU
That selected team's full schedule will display, along with the WIN and LOSS for each of their 16 games based on your picks.
The team's projected season win total is shown at the bottom of the schedule - based on Vegas lines.
MAIN MENU
*EVEN will display if the your total is equal to the projected total.*
Tap on the SEASON PREDICTION line to get a compiled record based on YOUR wins and losses- PLUS the OVER/UNDER notification, which will detail whether how your predictions compare with the Vegas line.
MAIN MENU
Changes to any week can be made by tapping on the desired Week, which will take you back to the selection screen. Make the necessary change and select SAVE CHANGES.
MAIN MENU
After modifying and resaving any picks, the team schedule must once again be accessed by from the STANDINGS menu.

The updated WIN and LOSS on the team schedule will display after reselecting the SEASON PROJECTION line.

*NOTE: You can also get the standings and weekly team results FOR A SINGLE TEAM without picking every single game by each team. Simply pick your team's games (from Week 1-17) in the MAKE PICKS section and SUBMIT. Only your team's record will display on the standings. Tab on the name to reveal their weekly schedule and results.
MAIN MENU
MY STATS

PICK TRACKER. Manually track your picks week to week. Simply enter your number of wins next to the week and select UPDATE. Your personal stats will calculate and yield results.
MAIN MENU
In addition to weekly stats, overall season totals will also be compiled.
At the conclusion of the regular season (and if inputted for all 17 weeks), the final season stats will display and yield results. See next.
MAIN MENU
Thank you for your support! Please inform us of any issues or concerns. Your feedback is important to us. Hope you enjoy!
